## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of the patent system's impact on inventiveness. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of patent laws and their interpretation means that the information may evolve over time, potentially affecting the relevance of the findings.